{"tid":1786902,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)活死人凶間 屍樂園1-2","createTime":"2019-12-17T13:35:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T19:01:59.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b7cafac1f5855f4f8d4434418d65cb5d83a8e4e1","tid":1786902,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T13:35:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">啊~~~死黑警~~~又唔做嘢又唔讀書</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=oGSqBYpvdEZZERTBUGrA0h3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=61007ea0\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=oGSqBYpvdEZZERTBUGrA0h3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=f73f3339\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OKRU 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=oGSqBYpvdEZZERTBUGrA0h3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=9a0428a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/a/a6/Dawn_Of_The_Dead.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fa%2Fa6%2FDawn_Of_The_Dead.jpg&h=df38f70c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/thumb/a/a3/Zombieland-poster.jpg/220px-Zombieland-poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fthumb%2Fa%2Fa3%2FZombieland-poster.jpg%2F220px-Zombieland-poster.jpg&h=ae3928c5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNDBkOTY5NzEtZmIxOC00YThlLWIyYTYtNWVlNjlhNTY3MzRiXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMDk2OTIwNQ@@._V1_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.media-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FM%2FMV5BNDBkOTY5NzEtZmIxOC00YThlLWIyYTYtNWVlNjlhNTY3MzRiXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMDk2OTIwNQ%40%40._V1_.jpg&h=d5dcece8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.一名居住在美國威斯康辛州密爾瓦基（Milwaukee）名叫安娜（Ana）的護士，在一如往常回到家休息。但隔天她的生活完全變了，丈夫變成了喪屍。好不容易開車逃離住宅，才知道整座城市已經陷入混亂，但突然有人要搶奪安娜的汽車，而撞上了一棵樹，安娜就暫時昏迷。（此時片頭音樂&quot;The Man Comes Around&quot;播放中，音樂還夾雜著各地因喪屍而陷入混亂的畫面） <br />\n<br />\n2.哥倫布(傑西伊森伯格)膽小如鼠一遇恐怖拔腿就逃，相反的泰拉哈斯(伍迪哈里遜)無所畏懼打遍天下無敵手，在一個被活屍所主宰的世界，這兩名完美倖存者終將遇到天敵─彼此..<br />\n<br />\n3.《屍樂園》續集，由原班人馬傑西艾森柏格、伍迪哈里遜、艾瑪史東回歸演出。柔弱的哥倫布、狠角色塔拉哈西、威奇塔和怪怪少女小石頭，四位主角將由白宮為核心出發展開一場如猶如漫畫大鬧般的虐殺旅<br />\n<br />\n10 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=oGSqBYpvdEZZERTBUGrA0h3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=84d133ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=oGSqBYpvdEZZERTBUGrA0h3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=32e84911\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca2b15967db416ac0640e06449d2a312aa1ba317","tid":1786902,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T13:39:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aba1c81bb8366d035f02717f52ddaea2a28f342a","tid":1786902,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T14:46:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09c22d5d9b880bef1454f0c0cc99d5cfef463e5e","tid":1786902,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T15:50:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e47f8267fa022e0796620896301959734b97f9a","tid":1786902,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T17:47:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa4b07f322aee02f44bed02a0fba6632bf0ed426","tid":1786902,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T19:01:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}